OL,5, The UK government has again given      
OL,6, emergency authorisation for the use of 
OL,7, a type of pesticide banned because of  
OL,8, the harm it can cause bees.            
OL,10,FPermission to use a neonicotinoid on   
OL,11,Fsugar beet seeds has been given to     
OL,12,Fprotect the crop from a particularly   
OL,13,Fdamaging virus spread by aphids.       
OL,15,FThe authorisation was given against the
OL,16,Fadvice of an independent panel of      
OL,17,Fpesticide experts.                     
OL,19,FCampaign group Friends of the Earth    
OL,20,Flabelled the move "incredibly brazen". 
